# Model diagnostics & comparison

This page showcase the model diagnosis and comparison for the E~max~ model 




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(tidyverse)
library(BayesERtools)
library(posterior)
library(tidybayes)
library(bayesplot)
library(loo)
library(here)
library(gt)

theme_set(theme_bw(base_size = 12))
```
:::






## Load data




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
d_example_emax_nocov <- read_csv(here("data", "d_example_emax_nocov.csv"))
```
:::




## Fit models

::: {.panel-tabset}

### Sigmoidal E~max~ model




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
set.seed(1234)

ermod_sigemax <- dev_ermod_emax(
  data = d_example_emax_nocov,
  var_resp = "Y",
  var_exposure = "Conc",
  gamma_fix = NULL
)

ermod_sigemax
```

